# Travel Guide App

A personalized travel guide app that connects users with curated guide personas based on shared tastes and background characteristics.

## Core Features
- User-Guide Matching System (Taste & Background Alignment)
- Personalized Guide Access
- "Right Now" Guided Recommendations
- Privacy-Focused Profile Matching

## Project Structure
- `/docs` - Documentation and planning
  - `app-idea.md` - Core concept and features
  - `ARCHITECTURE.md` - System design (coming soon)
  - `CONTRIBUTING.md` - Development guidelines (coming soon)
- `/prototype` - Design files and prototypes (coming soon)
  - `/flows` - User journey prototypes
  - `/components` - UI component designs

